#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "halt, poweroff, reboot - Halt, power-off or reboot the machine"
msgstr "halt, poweroff, reboot - Arrêter, éteindre ou redémarrer la machine"

#. type: SH
#: archlinux debian-bullseye debian-unstable fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron
#: opensuse-leap-15-3
#, no-wrap
msgid "SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "SYNOPSIS"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<halt> [OPTIONS...]"
msgstr "B<halt> [OPTIONS...]"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<poweroff> [OPTIONS...]"
msgstr "B<poweroff> [OPTIONS...]"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<reboot> [OPTIONS...]"
msgstr "B<reboot> [OPTIONS...]"

#. type: SH
#: archlinux debian-bullseye debian-unstable fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron
#: opensuse-leap-15-3
#, no-wrap
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "DESCRIPTION"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid ""
"B<halt>, B<poweroff>, B<reboot> may be used to halt, power-off, or reboot "
"the machine\\&. All three commands take the same options\\&."
msgstr ""
"B<halt>, B<poweroff>, B<reboot> peuvent être utilisées pour arrêter, "
"éteindre ou redémarrer la machine\\&. Ces trois commandes acceptent les "
"mêmes options\\&."

#. type: SH
#: archlinux debian-bullseye debian-unstable fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron
#: opensuse-leap-15-3
#, no-wrap
msgid "OPTIONS"
msgstr "OPTIONS"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "The following options are understood:"
msgstr "Les options suivantes sont comprises :"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<--help>"
msgstr "B<--help>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "Print a short help text and exit\\&."
msgstr "Afficher un aide-mémoire succinct et quitter\\&."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<--halt>"
msgstr "B<--halt>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid ""
"Halt the machine, regardless of which one of the three commands is invoked"
"\\&."
msgstr ""
"Arrêter la machine, sans tenir compte de laquelle des trois commandes est "
"invoquée\\&."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<-p>, B<--poweroff>"
msgstr "B<-p>, B<--poweroff>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid ""
"Power-off the machine, regardless of which one of the three commands is "
"invoked\\&."
msgstr ""
"Éteindre la machine, sans tenir compte de laquelle des trois commandes est "
"invoquée\\&."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<--reboot>"
msgstr "B<--reboot>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid ""
"Reboot the machine, regardless of which one of the three commands is invoked"
"\\&."
msgstr ""
"Redémarrer la machine, sans tenir compte de laquelle des trois commandes est "
"invoquée\\&."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<-f>, B<--force>"
msgstr "B<-f>, B<--force>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid ""
"Force immediate halt, power-off, or reboot\\&. When specified once, this "
"results in an immediate but clean shutdown by the system manager\\&. When "
"specified twice, this results in an immediate shutdown without contacting "
"the system manager\\&. See the description of B<--force> in B<systemctl>(1)  "
"for more details\\&."
msgstr ""
"Imposer immédiatement un arrêt, une extinction ou un redémarrage\\&. "
"Lorsqu’indiquée une seule fois, cela aboutit à une action propre du "
"gestionnaire du système\\&. Lorsqu’indiquée deux fois, cela aboutit à une "
"action immédiate sans contacter le gestionnaire du système\\&. Consulter la "
"description de B<--force> dans B<systemctl>(1) pour plus de détails\\&."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<-w>, B<--wtmp-only>"
msgstr "B<-w>, B<--wtmp-only>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid ""
"Only write wtmp shutdown entry, do not actually halt, power-off, reboot\\&."
msgstr ""
"Écrire seulement l’entrée d’interruption dans le fichier B<wtmp>, ne pas "
"réaliser l’arrêt, l’extinction ou le redémarrage\\&."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<-d>, B<--no-wtmp>"
msgstr "B<-d>, B<--no-wtmp>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "Do not write wtmp shutdown entry\\&."
msgstr "Ne pas écrire l’entrée d’interruption dans le fichier I<wtmp>\\&."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<-n>, B<--no-sync>"
msgstr "B<-n>, B<--no-sync>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid ""
"Don\\*(Aqt sync hard disks/storage media before halt, power-off, reboot\\&."
msgstr ""
"Ne pas synchroniser les disques durs ou les médias de stockage avant "
"l’arrêt, l’extinction ou le redémarrage\\&."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<--no-wall>"
msgstr "B<--no-wall>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "Do not send wall message before halt, power-off, reboot\\&."
msgstr ""
"Ne pas envoyer de message d’avertissement avant l’arrêt, l’extinction ou le "
"redémarrage\\&."

#. type: SH
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
#, no-wrap
msgid "EXIT STATUS"
msgstr "CODE DE RETOUR"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "On success, 0 is returned, a non-zero failure code otherwise\\&."
msgstr ""
"En cas de succès, B<0> est renvoyé, autrement, un code d'échec non nul est "
"renvoyé\\&."

#. type: SH
#: archlinux debian-bullseye debian-unstable fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron
#: opensuse-leap-15-3
#, no-wrap
msgid "NOTES"
msgstr "NOTES"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid ""
"These commands are implemented in a way that preserves basic compatibility "
"with the original SysV commands\\&.  B<systemctl>(1)  verbs B<halt>, "
"B<poweroff>, B<reboot> provide the same functionality with some additional "
"features\\&."
msgstr ""
"Ces commandes sont implémentées de façon à préserver une compatibilité "
"basique avec les commandes originelles de SysV\\&. Les termes B<halt>, "
"B<poweroff> et B<reboot> de B<systemctl>(1) fournissent les mêmes fonctions "
"avec quelques fonctionnalités supplémentaires\\&."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid ""
"Note that on many SysV systems B<halt> used to be synonymous to B<poweroff>, "
"i\\&.e\\&. both commands would equally result in powering the machine off"
"\\&. systemd is more accurate here, and B<halt> results in halting the "
"machine only (leaving power on), and B<poweroff> is required to actually "
"power it off\\&."
msgstr ""
"Remarquez que sur beaucoup de systèmes SysV, B<halt> était habituellement un "
"synonyme de B<poweroff>, c'est-à-dire que les deux commandes aboutissaient à "
"l’extinction de la machine\\&. Systemd sur ce sujet est plus précis. B<halt> "
"conduit seulement à l’arrêt de la machine (toujours sous tension) et "
"B<poweroff> est nécessaire pour l’éteindre réellement\\&."

